data.description: Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, 3 Full bath home with a 2car garage, boasting CBS construction completed in 2022. Rest easy knowing the property is equipped with full shutters for hurricane protection. Enjoy outdoor living with a fenced yard featuring a covered patio and cabana bath, plus ample space for a pool - perfect for entertaining or relaxing in privacy! Nature lovers will delight in the proximity to White City Park, offering a kayak and canoe launch! Experience the delights of Downtown Ft. Pierce with its green market, restaurants, marina, beaches, and shopping just 20 min away! Conveniently located, this home offers easy access to major routes- ideal for commuters. Explore St. Lucie West for a variety of shopping and dining options, and catch a game or event at Met Stadium! Golf enthusiasts will appreciate being mere minutes from St. James Golf Course. Experience the best of Florida living in this well-appointed home in a prime location!
